<h2> Checkup successful install
</h2>

On every server referenced in `[INSTALL_SERVER]`, execute checks to validated proper applicative installation :

* Tomcat Server is properly running (if the server is not started, then it shall be started).

* Tomcat Server is listening on port defined in configuration files for variables `TOMCAT_HTTP_PORT`, `TOMCAT_HTTPS_PORT` and `TOMCAT_SHUTDOWN_PORT`.

* Deployed WebApplication are properly deployed on Tomcat Server .

* Apache Httpd is properly running and is listening on port `80` & `443`.

Note that these checks are not sufficient to declare the installation complete. 
Tests need to be achieved by Dev Team once every IT equipments will be installed, upgrade, migrate, up and running.
